Also, I think the reason Mitoko is going along should be clear.  I think the easiest reason is that she feels somehow guilty for aiding evil, and needs redemption of some sort.  Same thing with Patrick, since he apparently has killed someone innocent.  And Alex, obviously, wants to know what the hell is going on.<br>
